  help: An empty table has no effect. Use `<channel> = false` to disable the mapping for this channel, or `<channel> = { mapping-mode = "replace" }` to skip the default mapping data. The same-name
        heuristic keeps its per-channel default (on for conda-forge, off otherwise) unless you set `same-name-heuristic`.
